NVCN Joke of the dayA man walks into a bar and sits down Before he can say anything the jerk next to him flags the bartender down and says Hey Jacka give me a drink and the bartender does in silenceTaking note of this rudeness and feeling for the bartender he pipes in and yells Sir when you find a moment could I have a pint please hoping the man at the bar takes note of his kindness The bartender nods kindly and brings it20 minutes later the jerk yells at the bartender again Hey Jacka another round The bartender quietly obligesAfter around 3 more of these berating interactions the jerk pays his tab and stumbles home while the bartender maintains his professional silenceConcerned about the bartender the man flags him over and asks Why do you tolerate him calling you Jacka Thats not very niceTo which the bartender finally speaks and replies W w well He Aw He Aw h heh He Always calls me thatShow More
